                },
                "self": {
                    "href": "https://api.github.com/repos/neovim/neovim/pulls/comments/3107607569"
                }
            },
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "i don't think notify() gives any hint about where it comes from, so it's usually good to have a prefix like \"lsp: ...\".\n\nthe error number is E849 so let's mention that at least https://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/f2cc0a249d20462619801a194b67f6ab1d48476c/src/nvim/highlight_group.c#L2097\n\n```suggestion\n    vim.notify_once('E849: The maximum number of highlight groups has been reached.', vim.log.levels.WARN)\n```",
            "commit_id": "73243fb2457f5044f8afd47ccc38598ee4a10f0e",
            "created_at": "2026-04-19T22:29:11Z",
            "diff_hunk": "@@ -86,6 +86,7 @@ local function get_hl_group(hex_code, style)\n   -- Limit number of created highlight groups to 10000 to not approach near\n   -- a hard limit of 19999 highlight groups (`:h E849`)\n   if n_color_cache > 10000 then\n+    vim.notify_once('The maximum number of highlight groups has been reached.', vim.log.levels.WARN)",
